<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PiliPili</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/testflight.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <h1>iOS安装步骤</h1>
    <div class="corner-bg">
        <span class="orange-text">下载前必看</span>
    </div>
    <span class="orange-text">请用苹果的Safari浏览器进行下载，其他浏览器可能无法正常下载</span>
    <span class="gray-text">請仔細閱讀完【安裝步驟】後再操作</span>
    <div class="guide-container">
        <div class="guide-item">
            <span class="s-title">第一步</span>
            <img class="s-img" src="images/tf-logo.png" alt="tf-logo">
            <div class="corner-bg">
                <span class="s-des">安装Test Flight</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <img id="org-arrow" src="images/org-arrow.png" alt="org-a">
        <div class="guide-item">
            <span class="s-title">第二步</span>
            <img class="s-img" src="images/pp-logo.png" alt="pp-logo">
            <div class="corner-bg">
                <span class="s-des">安装PiliPili</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="step-container">
        <div class="s-item">
            <span class="s-item-title">第一步</span>
            <span class="s-item-des">點擊安裝<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/testflight/id899247664" target="_blank">TestFlight</a>，如已安裝，要記得返回本頁進行第二步操作。若已安装，直接进行第二步。</span>
            <div class="s-item-ex">
                <span class="s-item-ex-title">示例图1</span>
                <img class="s-item-ex-img" src="images/appstore-tf.png" alt="appstore-tf">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="s-item">
            <span class="s-item-title">第二步</span>
            <span class="s-item-des">點擊下載官方版 <a href=<%= url %> target="_blank">PiliPili</a>。然後在TestFlight內安裝</span>
            <div class="s-item-ex">
                <span class="s-item-ex-title">示例图2</span>
                <img class="s-item-ex-img" src="images/appstore-pp.png" alt="appstore-pp">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://s9.cnzz.com/z_stat.php?id=1280292624&web_id=1280292624"></script>
</body>

</html>